#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.95"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.95:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.95:0.2"
msgid "10. Āhuneyyavagga"
msgstr "10. Worthy of Offerings"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.95:0.3"
msgid "95"
msgstr "95"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.146"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.95:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattime, bhikkhave, puggalā āhuneyyā … pe … dakkhiṇeyyā añjalikaraṇīyā "
"anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are seven people worthy of offerings dedicated to the "
"gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s offering, and worthy of "
"greeting with joined palms. They are a supreme field of merit for the world."

msgctxt "an7.95:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.95:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo cakkhusmiṃ aniccānupassī viharati "
"aniccasaññī aniccapaṭisaṃvedī satataṃ samitaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ cetasā "
"adhimuccamāno paññāya pariyogāhamāno."
msgstr ""
"First, take a person who meditates observing impermanence in the eye. They "
"perceive impermanence and experience impermanence. Constantly, continually, "
"and without stopping, they apply the mind and fathom with wisdom."

msgctxt "an7.95:1.4"
msgid ""
"So āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ "
"abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"They realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this "
"very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due to "
"the ending of defilements."

msgctxt "an7.95:1.5"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, paṭhamo puggalo āhuneyyo pāhuneyyo … pe … anuttaraṃ "
"puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""
"This is the first person worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy "
"of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s offering, and worthy of greeting with "
"joined palms. They are a supreme field of merit for the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.95:2.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco puggalo cakkhusmiṃ aniccānupassī viharati "
"aniccasaññī aniccapaṭisaṃvedī satataṃ samitaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ cetasā "
"adhimuccamāno paññāya pariyogāhamāno."
msgstr "Next, take a person who meditates observing impermanence in the eye. …"

msgctxt "an7.95:2.2"
msgid "Tassa apubbaṃ acarimaṃ āsavapariyādānañca hoti jīvitapariyādānañca."
msgstr ""
"Their defilements and their life come to an end at exactly the same time."

msgctxt "an7.95:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo puggalo āhuneyyo … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ "
"lokassa."
msgstr "This is the second person worthy of offerings …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.95:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco puggalo cakkhusmiṃ aniccānupassī viharati "
"aniccasaññī aniccapaṭisaṃvedī satataṃ samitaṃ abbokiṇṇaṃ cetasā "
"adhimuccamāno paññāya pariyogāhamāno."
msgstr "Next, take a person who meditates observing impermanence in the eye. …"

msgctxt "an7.95:3.2"
msgid ""
"So pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā antarāparinibbāyī hoti … "
"pe …"
msgstr ""
"With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished in-between "
"one life and the next. …"

msgctxt "an7.95:3.3"
msgid "upahaccaparinibbāyī hoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished upon landing. "
"…"

msgctxt "an7.95:3.4"
msgid "asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished without extra "
"effort. …"

msgctxt "an7.95:3.5"
msgid "sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"With the ending of the five lower fetters they’re extinguished with extra "
"effort. …"

msgctxt "an7.95:3.6"
msgid "uddhaṃsoto hoti akaniṭṭhagāmī."
msgstr ""
"With the ending of the five lower fetters they head upstream, going to the "
"Akaniṭṭha realm. …"

msgctxt "an7.95:3.7"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, sattamo puggalo āhuneyyo … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ "
"lokassa."
msgstr "This is the seventh person."

msgctxt "an7.95:3.8"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, satta puggalā āhuneyyā pāhuneyyā dakkhiṇeyyā "
"añjalikaraṇīyā anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These seven people are worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of "
"hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s offering, and worthy of greeting with "
"joined palms. They are a supreme field of merit for the world.”"
